reviews.review:
Visited for my second time yesterday.  The spot is tucked away in the northwest part of the valley.  The cupcakes are very good.  Incredibly moist even at closing time.  This can always be a problem  I will say they put on quite a large dollop of frosting, which while pretty tasty is incredibly sweet.  We also tried a sugar cookie which was also incredible.

The girls behind the counter were attentive and friendly, and you could tell they enojyed what they were doing.

Looking forward to maybe getting my next birthday cake there;
